1
00:00:09,526 --> 00:00:10,288
<i>C'mon!</i>

2
00:00:16,833 --> 00:00:19,427
<i>Running like a fugitive,</i>

3
00:00:20,470 --> 00:00:22,631
<i>Being chased by something</i>

4
00:00:24,307 --> 00:00:26,969
<i>Inside my heart is pounding</i>

5
00:00:28,078 --> 00:00:30,706
<i>My throat dry like it's withering</i>

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:35,509
<i>For no single one,</i>

7
00:00:36,019 --> 00:00:39,284
<i>To none does belong,</i>

8
00:00:40,757 --> 00:00:45,023
<i>This time is ours, right now...</i>

9
00:00:47,664 --> 00:00:49,529
<i>Unraveling the pain,</i>

10
00:00:49,633 --> 00:00:51,362
<i>Unraveling our hearts,</i>

11
00:00:51,434 --> 00:00:53,766
<i>Unraveling shadows</i>

12
00:00:55,305 --> 00:00:57,068
<i>Stifling our breath,</i>

13
00:00:57,140 --> 00:00:59,040
<i>Reaching for beyond,</i>

14
00:00:59,109 --> 00:01:01,543
<i>Tearing through the dark</i>

15
00:01:03,446 --> 00:01:10,010
<i>In fighting and in love</i>

16
00:01:10,987 --> 00:01:13,615
<i>To the distant light above,</i>

17
00:01:14,057 --> 00:01:17,254
<i>Yes, we are on the way</i>

18
00:01:21,931 --> 00:01:23,296
<i>I wanna rock...</i>

19
00:01:25,869 --> 00:01:27,393
<i>Rockin' my heart</i>

20
00:02:02,676 --> 00:02:05,144
Today's... a special day, so...

21
00:02:07,481 --> 00:02:08,675
Time to eat!

22
00:02:18,125 --> 00:02:20,184
<i>Sasuke and Sakura. Friends or Foes?</i>

23
00:02:54,928 --> 00:02:56,225
Fight me, here!

24
00:03:00,167 --> 00:03:02,465
What're you doing, Konohamaru?

25
00:03:03,237 --> 00:03:04,898
Very good, Naruto...

26
00:03:05,672 --> 00:03:07,867
You're the man I expected you to be.

27
00:03:10,844 --> 00:03:12,539
I didn't do anything, you know...

28
00:03:13,714 --> 00:03:15,443
Let's fight fair!

29
00:03:16,049 --> 00:03:18,711
Sorry! I've got
an orientation meeting to go to.

30
00:03:19,720 --> 00:03:20,880
An orientation meeting?

31
00:03:21,288 --> 00:03:23,848
Cause... As of today, I'm a Ninja!

32
00:03:25,893 --> 00:03:26,416
Oh...

33
00:03:42,843 --> 00:03:45,971
Sakura!
Shouldn't you be heading out soon?

34
00:03:47,281 --> 00:03:49,010
I was thinking of leaving now!

35
00:03:50,350 --> 00:03:54,184
Cha! How long are you planning
to treat me like a child?!

36
00:03:58,525 --> 00:04:01,688
<i>That's right... I'm not a student</i>
<i>of the academy anymore...</i>

37
00:04:02,930 --> 00:04:05,865
I'm a Kunoichi of the Leaf Village,
Sakura Haruno!

38
00:04:06,500 --> 00:04:07,467
I'm off!

39
00:04:15,475 --> 00:04:16,737
Morning, Sakura.

40
00:04:17,644 --> 00:04:18,906
Morning... Ino.

41
00:04:26,620 --> 00:04:29,418
Who would've thought you'd
be able to graduate.

42
00:04:29,857 --> 00:04:31,791
Ancient history has nothing to do with it.

43
00:04:32,159 --> 00:04:34,491
As of today,
we're both full fledged Ninjas...

44
00:04:35,896 --> 00:04:37,295
I won't lose to you anymore, Ino!

45
00:04:58,952 --> 00:05:01,682
What the? Why are you here?

46
00:05:02,189 --> 00:05:04,657
Today's meeting is for graduates only.

47
00:05:05,492 --> 00:05:09,360
Hey, don't you see this headband?

48
00:05:10,163 --> 00:05:12,757
As of today, I'm a Ninja, too!

49
00:05:14,701 --> 00:05:18,899
How can I put it, it really suits me.

50
00:05:21,108 --> 00:05:23,668
<i>So Naruto... was able to graduate.</i>

51
00:05:33,387 --> 00:05:34,513
Goal!

52
00:05:37,357 --> 00:05:39,120
I won again, Sakura!

53
00:05:39,359 --> 00:05:40,485
What're you saying?

54
00:05:40,661 --> 00:05:44,324
The tip of my foot got in
one centimeter faster!

55
00:05:44,965 --> 00:05:46,626
You must be blind.

56
00:05:48,068 --> 00:05:49,296
<i>It's Sakura.</i>

57
00:05:53,974 --> 00:05:54,497
Oh...

58
00:05:56,376 --> 00:05:58,571
<i>Sakura's looking at me...</i>

59
00:06:00,881 --> 00:06:01,848
Hey, Sakura!

60
00:06:02,182 --> 00:06:03,979
Mor... morning, Sakur

61
00:06:04,051 --> 00:06:04,915
Get outta' the way!

62
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:08,212
M-Morning, Sasuke...

63
00:06:12,359 --> 00:06:13,951
Mind if I sit next to you?

64
00:06:14,895 --> 00:06:17,693
Hey! <i>I'm</i> going to sit
next to Sasuke!

65
00:06:17,798 --> 00:06:19,129
First come, first served!

66
00:06:19,666 --> 00:06:22,396
<i>I got in the classroom sooner!</i>

67
00:06:22,803 --> 00:06:23,326
I did!

68
00:06:23,403 --> 00:06:24,768
If that's the case,
then I did!

69
00:06:24,838 --> 00:06:25,736
I was first!

70
00:06:26,206 --> 00:06:28,037
<i>I'm</i> sitting next to Sasuke!

71
00:06:30,610 --> 00:06:31,577
<i>How annoying...</i>

72
00:06:33,447 --> 00:06:38,009
Is that this year's top rookie,
Sasuke Uchiha?

73
00:06:38,852 --> 00:06:39,580
Yes.

74
00:06:41,121 --> 00:06:43,487
The sole survivor of the Uchiha clan?

75
00:06:44,825 --> 00:06:45,621
Yes.

76
00:06:56,169 --> 00:06:58,433
Naruto Uzumaki, eh...

77
00:07:11,051 --> 00:07:14,179
Naruto! Don't glare at Sasuke!

78
00:07:15,922 --> 00:07:17,048
<i>Sakura...</i>

79
00:07:18,125 --> 00:07:20,650
<i>Everyone's all Sasuke Sasuke.</i>

80
00:07:21,094 --> 00:07:22,823
<i>What's so great about this guy?!</i>

81
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:29,100
Just beat him up, Sasuke!

82
00:07:29,269 --> 00:07:30,201
Yeah! Yeah!

83
00:07:30,804 --> 00:07:32,704
What? Really?

84
00:07:32,939 --> 00:07:34,065
Oh! Sorry!

85
00:07:34,574 --> 00:07:35,040
Wha?

86
00:07:35,876 --> 00:07:36,501
Whoa!

87
00:07:44,951 --> 00:07:50,912
Cha! <i>I was planning on</i>
seizing Sasuke's first kiss!

88
00:07:54,394 --> 00:07:56,362
You jerk...
Naruto! I'll kill you!

89
00:07:56,663 --> 00:07:58,460
- My mouth is rotting.
- Huh? Was that my fault?

90
00:07:59,566 --> 00:08:01,363
What? I feel rage...

91
00:08:03,503 --> 00:08:04,470
Naruto...

92
00:08:05,305 --> 00:08:06,636
You...

93
00:08:07,007 --> 00:08:09,066
An accident...
It was an accident

94
00:08:11,144 --> 00:08:11,974
You are annoying!

95
00:08:12,679 --> 00:08:13,270
Yikes!

96
00:08:14,881 --> 00:08:19,341
Naruto... He's at
the center of trouble as usual.

97
00:08:20,654 --> 00:08:25,148
As of today, you all have become
full fledged Ninjas...

98
00:08:25,892 --> 00:08:27,826
However, you're still Genin.

99
00:08:28,895 --> 00:08:30,795
The tough part's still to come!

100
00:08:31,865 --> 00:08:34,629
From here on, you'll be in a squad of three

101
00:08:34,801 --> 00:08:38,032
and carry out your missions
under your Jonin teachers.

102
00:08:40,807 --> 00:08:41,933
<i>A squad of three?!</i>

103
00:08:42,642 --> 00:08:45,668
I wonder who's going to be
grouped with Sasuke.

104
00:08:46,913 --> 00:08:47,709
I don't know...

105
00:08:49,549 --> 00:08:53,576
Cha! I'll be the one grouped
with Sasuke, naturally!

106
00:08:55,755 --> 00:09:00,192
<i>Squads of three, eh.</i>
<i>It'll just slow me down...</i>

107
00:09:01,027 --> 00:09:02,619
<i>First will be Sakura.</i>

108
00:09:02,796 --> 00:09:03,888
<i>And the other person...</i>

109
00:09:05,432 --> 00:09:07,195
<i>can be anyone other than Sasuke!</i>

110
00:09:07,968 --> 00:09:09,731
The groups have been determined

111
00:09:09,803 --> 00:09:12,533
so that the strength of
the groups will be balanced.

112
00:09:13,273 --> 00:09:14,763
Now for the assignments!

113
00:09:18,578 --> 00:09:19,772
Now then, next is Group Seven...

114
00:09:20,547 --> 00:09:21,707
Naruto Uzumaki!

115
00:09:23,116 --> 00:09:24,140
Sakura Haruno.

116
00:09:26,052 --> 00:09:27,144
Hooray!

117
00:09:27,587 --> 00:09:29,179
I'm with... Naruto?

118
00:09:29,890 --> 00:09:31,414
And... Sasuke Uchiha!

119
00:09:31,925 --> 00:09:33,051
Hooray!

120
00:09:33,660 --> 00:09:35,150
I'm with... Sasuke?

121
00:09:39,366 --> 00:09:41,664
<i>So I'll be in a different group</i>
<i>from Naruto, huh...</i>

122
00:09:42,936 --> 00:09:45,200
Next is Group Eight. Hinata Hyuga!

123
00:09:45,338 --> 00:09:47,101
Y-Yes...

124
00:09:47,807 --> 00:09:48,831
Kiba Inuzuka!

125
00:09:50,343 --> 00:09:51,367
Shino Aburame!

126
00:09:56,149 --> 00:09:57,639
Why is this happening?

127
00:09:58,251 --> 00:09:58,945
Group Nine.

128
00:09:59,052 --> 00:10:01,520
Cha! Love will be victorious!

129
00:10:02,856 --> 00:10:03,550
Man...

130
00:10:04,191 --> 00:10:07,854
Why do women think that
kind of guy's so great?

131
00:10:08,428 --> 00:10:11,363
Don't you understand, Shikamaru?

132
00:10:12,165 --> 00:10:14,099
Well, I'm not a woman...

133
00:10:16,703 --> 00:10:18,534
That's why you are
not popular among girls.

134
00:10:19,039 --> 00:10:22,031
I wouldn't want to be grouped with you.

135
00:10:23,176 --> 00:10:28,409
Group Ten. Ino Yamanaka.
Shikamaru Nara.

136
00:10:29,082 --> 00:10:30,982
It appears we've been
grouped together.

137
00:10:33,253 --> 00:10:35,813
And Choji Akimichi.

138
00:10:39,659 --> 00:10:41,456
<i>And Fatty on top of that...</i>

139
00:10:44,197 --> 00:10:45,255
That's all for the group division.

140
00:10:45,465 --> 00:10:46,693
Iruka Sensei!

141
00:10:47,367 --> 00:10:48,800
Why does an exceptional student
like me have to be

142
00:10:48,868 --> 00:10:50,893
in the same group with this guy?!

143
00:10:52,772 --> 00:10:55,673
Sasuke has the best grades
of the graduates.

144
00:10:56,710 --> 00:10:58,507
Naruto, you're at the bottom!

145
00:10:59,546 --> 00:11:03,539
Of course, this is how it is when trying
to balance the strength within groups.

146
00:11:04,517 --> 00:11:07,714
Just don't get in my way, loser!

147
00:11:09,256 --> 00:11:10,587
Hey, what did you say?!

148
00:11:10,890 --> 00:11:11,788
You want to fight, loser?

149
00:11:12,926 --> 00:11:14,325
Knock it off, Naruto!!

150
00:11:16,730 --> 00:11:19,096
In the afternoon,
I'll introduce you to your Jonin teachers.

151
00:11:19,499 --> 00:11:20,557
You're dismissed until then!

152
00:11:22,335 --> 00:11:23,529
Sasuke!

153
00:11:24,237 --> 00:11:26,398
Where'd you go, Sasuke?

154
00:11:27,540 --> 00:11:32,273
I thought since we're in the same group
and all, we'd eat together.

155
00:11:32,479 --> 00:11:33,946
Sakuraaaa!

156
00:11:34,247 --> 00:11:37,978
Since we're in the same group and all,
let's eat together!

157
00:11:38,618 --> 00:11:41,849
Why should I have to eat with you?!

158
00:11:42,122 --> 00:11:44,989
Well... we're in the same group, so...

159
00:11:45,292 --> 00:11:47,157
You're... annoying.

160
00:11:50,096 --> 00:11:52,155
Sasuke! Where are you?

161
00:12:00,373 --> 00:12:01,965
<i>Damn! This is no fun.</i>

162
00:12:02,709 --> 00:12:05,610
<i>I'm finally in the same group as Sakura...</i>
<i>and then it's like this...</i>

163
00:12:06,479 --> 00:12:08,606
I wonder if something good will happen...

164
00:12:18,191 --> 00:12:18,885
That's it!

165
00:12:28,262 --> 00:12:29,092
Listen up!

166
00:12:29,196 --> 00:12:32,962
As long as we're in the same group,
you will follow my instructions.

167
00:12:33,734 --> 00:12:34,758
Yeah yeah...

168
00:12:36,036 --> 00:12:39,369
<i>She becomes a real pain in the neck</i>
<i>when people try to argue with to her, so...</i>

169
00:12:39,807 --> 00:12:42,071
Let's all go out for
some BBQ sometime.

170
00:12:42,343 --> 00:12:42,832
Oh, man...

171
00:12:44,245 --> 00:12:44,734
Hmm?

172
00:12:49,283 --> 00:12:50,079
Naruto?

173
00:12:50,317 --> 00:12:50,874
Huh?

174
00:12:53,854 --> 00:12:54,582
Oh!

175
00:12:56,457 --> 00:12:57,651
Jerk, it's Naruto, isn't it!

176
00:12:57,725 --> 00:12:59,352
Damn! Just be quiet.

177
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:03,753
Naruto! I won't forgive you
if you hurt Sasuke!

178
00:13:11,806 --> 00:13:12,864
What happened?

179
00:13:16,977 --> 00:13:18,535
Heh! Idiot...

180
00:13:25,252 --> 00:13:27,550
So Naruto got beaten by
the one he challenged...

181
00:13:28,889 --> 00:13:32,882
Of course! Naruto's no match
for Sasuke!

182
00:13:37,298 --> 00:13:38,526
<i>No need for me to feel rushed...</i>

183
00:13:39,266 --> 00:13:40,528
<i>From here on out,</i>

184
00:13:40,601 --> 00:13:42,125
<i>I'll be in the same group as</i>
<i>Sasuke for the long haul...</i>

185
00:13:44,438 --> 00:13:44,870
<i>But...</i>

186
00:13:49,777 --> 00:13:51,438
<i>Even if I were to use</i>
<i>my feminine charms...</i>

187
00:13:51,679 --> 00:13:53,510
<i>my proportions are below average...</i>

188
00:13:54,381 --> 00:13:56,508
<i>All that's above average is</i>
<i>the width of my forehead...</i>

189
00:13:57,551 --> 00:13:58,575
<i>What should I do?</i>

190
00:14:02,923 --> 00:14:04,220
<i>Huh? No way!</i>

191
00:14:05,025 --> 00:14:05,923
<i>Sasuke... is looking...</i>

192
00:14:05,993 --> 00:14:07,017
<i>this way!</i>

193
00:14:09,997 --> 00:14:11,965
<i>And with such a passionate look!</i>

194
00:14:13,601 --> 00:14:17,059
<i>You... have a charmingly wide forehead.</i>

195
00:14:17,872 --> 00:14:20,204
<i>It makes me want to kiss it.</i>

196
00:14:21,375 --> 00:14:23,240
<i>That's what its surface area is for.</i>

197
00:14:25,212 --> 00:14:26,179
<i>Yeah, right...</i>

198
00:14:27,448 --> 00:14:29,780
<i>I'm not just some kid</i>
<i>who believes in fairy tales...</i>

199
00:14:30,417 --> 00:14:31,679
<i>There's no way.</i>

200
00:14:32,453 --> 00:14:35,320
You... have a charmingly wide forehead.

201
00:14:35,923 --> 00:14:36,355
What?!

202
00:14:38,659 --> 00:14:40,354
It makes me want to kiss it.

203
00:14:47,968 --> 00:14:50,937
Cha! This fairy tale is for real!!

204
00:14:51,972 --> 00:14:55,271
Or that's what Naruto would say.

205
00:14:57,578 --> 00:14:59,170
I've got something to ask you.

206
00:15:00,047 --> 00:15:00,513
What?

207
00:15:01,849 --> 00:15:04,340
What do you think... of Naruto?

208
00:15:06,887 --> 00:15:13,315
He's quite at home interfering and
enjoys it when I make mistakes.

209
00:15:14,428 --> 00:15:18,057
Naruto doesn't understand
one thing about me...

210
00:15:20,234 --> 00:15:21,201
He just annoys me!

211
00:15:22,436 --> 00:15:26,930
All I want... is for you to
accept me, Sasuke...

212
00:15:28,342 --> 00:15:30,173
For me to accept you?

213
00:15:32,279 --> 00:15:35,680
I'll do anything for the sake of that.

214
00:15:46,927 --> 00:15:47,985
<i>I was careless!</i>

215
00:15:56,470 --> 00:15:56,936
<i>W-Wha?!</i>

216
00:15:59,807 --> 00:16:00,831
<i>Gotcha!</i>

217
00:16:04,278 --> 00:16:06,906
<i>I didn't think someone who couldn't</i>
<i>perform the Clone Jutsu properly</i>

218
00:16:07,181 --> 00:16:10,742
<i>could do the Shadow Clone Jutsu.</i>

219
00:16:15,089 --> 00:16:17,284
I'm... desperate, so...

220
00:16:19,026 --> 00:16:20,994
<i>I finally know why I...</i>

221
00:16:22,563 --> 00:16:25,794
<i>I like Sakura so much.</i>

222
00:16:30,137 --> 00:16:31,934
<i>Diarrhea at a time like this?!</i>

223
00:16:34,341 --> 00:16:35,103
What's wrong?

224
00:16:36,243 --> 00:16:37,904
I-I'll be right back...

225
00:16:39,246 --> 00:16:41,476
Sasuke's so shy!

226
00:16:42,883 --> 00:16:44,942
I guess he needs to
prepare himself mentally...

227
00:16:51,558 --> 00:16:52,752
That was close!

228
00:16:53,460 --> 00:16:56,952
My stomach hurt so much that
the Jutsu was about to wear off!

229
00:16:57,531 --> 00:17:00,932
Why does my stomach have
to hurt at such a good time?!

230
00:17:03,370 --> 00:17:04,462
<i>I'm annoying... huh...</i>

231
00:17:05,572 --> 00:17:07,096
<i>She said so again...</i>

232
00:17:07,875 --> 00:17:11,038
<i>And I transformed into Sasuke and</i>
<i>had got a little closer to Sakura...</i>

233
00:17:13,080 --> 00:17:16,208
In that case...
I'll play an obnoxious Sasuke...

234
00:17:16,717 --> 00:17:19,481
and make her hate him!

235
00:17:25,426 --> 00:17:29,362
Oh Sasuke,
you're such a shy bad boy!

236
00:17:30,164 --> 00:17:34,396
Are you prepared? I'm raring to go!

237
00:17:35,569 --> 00:17:37,400
H-Hey, Sasuke!

238
00:17:40,107 --> 00:17:40,801
Where's Naruto?

239
00:17:41,175 --> 00:17:43,803
Oh, there you go changing
the subject again...

240
00:17:44,144 --> 00:17:46,442
Just leave Naruto alone!

241
00:17:47,047 --> 00:17:49,709
All he does is pick fights with you!

242
00:17:49,983 --> 00:17:53,282
It's because he wasn't raised right!

243
00:17:53,954 --> 00:17:54,613
You know!

244
00:17:54,688 --> 00:17:56,588
He doesn't have any parents, right?

245
00:17:57,891 --> 00:18:00,257
He always selfishly does
whatever he wants!

246
00:18:00,594 --> 00:18:04,052
My parents would get mad at me
if I did something like that!

247
00:18:05,065 --> 00:18:08,831
There are no parents to nag you
if it's just you alone!

248
00:18:09,203 --> 00:18:11,831
So his selfishness comes
out at various times!

249
00:18:13,307 --> 00:18:14,035
The loneliness.

250
00:18:14,408 --> 00:18:14,965
Huh?

251
00:18:16,443 --> 00:18:19,344
It's something worse than getting
scolded by parents and...

252
00:18:21,014 --> 00:18:22,413
W-What's gotten into you?

253
00:18:24,251 --> 00:18:25,047
You...

254
00:18:25,352 --> 00:18:26,182
annoy me.

255
00:18:37,531 --> 00:18:40,364
Damn! It finally stopped!

256
00:18:41,702 --> 00:18:43,932
I wonder if Sakura's still waiting.

257
00:18:50,277 --> 00:18:52,370
W-What are you doing here?!

258
00:18:52,679 --> 00:18:56,342
I used the Escape Jutsu,
the very basic of techniques.

259
00:18:56,884 --> 00:18:57,282
Oh...

260
00:18:57,718 --> 00:18:58,878
What were you planning to do...

261
00:18:58,952 --> 00:19:00,146
by transforming into me?!

262
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:03,150
I thought it'd be fun, so I gave it a try!

263
00:19:08,462 --> 00:19:09,895
The Shadow Clone Jutsu again?!

264
00:19:10,130 --> 00:19:11,995
I'll show you that I'm really amazing!

265
00:19:12,132 --> 00:19:13,599
I'll defeat you...

266
00:19:13,667 --> 00:19:15,601
and make you accept me!

267
00:19:16,136 --> 00:19:17,865
Prepare yourself, Sasuke!

268
00:19:23,410 --> 00:19:24,809
Just like that, my stomach again...

269
00:19:26,346 --> 00:19:27,711
B-Bathroom!

270
00:19:29,583 --> 00:19:30,413
I'm first, I say!

271
00:19:30,784 --> 00:19:31,512
I'm first, I say.

272
00:19:31,585 --> 00:19:33,280
I'm about to go in my pants, I say!

273
00:19:36,356 --> 00:19:37,414
How stupid!

274
00:19:40,727 --> 00:19:41,989
<i>"You annoy me"...huh?</i>

275
00:19:43,330 --> 00:19:47,733
<i>I see. So this is how</i>
<i>Naruto must've felt...</i>

276
00:19:49,036 --> 00:19:53,473
I wonder if I can...
be a bit more nice next time...

277
00:19:54,675 --> 00:19:55,869
Damn.

278
00:19:56,410 --> 00:19:58,435
Did I eat something bad?

279
00:19:59,246 --> 00:20:00,008
<i>Naruto...</i>

280
00:20:02,049 --> 00:20:03,243
<i>Smile... Smile...</i>

281
00:20:05,385 --> 00:20:07,410
Let's go back to the classroom, Naruto.

282
00:20:08,155 --> 00:20:09,087
Sakura...

283
00:20:11,858 --> 00:20:13,758
<i>Payback for earlier, huh?</i>

284
00:20:13,827 --> 00:20:16,022
<i>Sasuke's turned himself into Sakura...</i>

285
00:20:16,964 --> 00:20:19,057
You're trying to trick me, right, Sasuke?!

286
00:20:19,299 --> 00:20:20,357
I don't think so!

287
00:20:24,238 --> 00:20:27,264
Ow ow ow...
What the heck is going on?!

288
00:20:28,842 --> 00:20:29,399
Oh...

289
00:20:33,113 --> 00:20:35,707
You idiot, Naruto!

290
00:20:41,154 --> 00:20:43,054
So, this is Naruto's room...

291
00:20:43,657 --> 00:20:47,821
And Sasuke of the Uchiha clan is
also in the group you'll be in charge of.

292
00:20:48,161 --> 00:20:49,355
I wish you good luck!

293
00:20:54,101 --> 00:20:55,466
<i>The expiration date...</i>

294
00:20:56,169 --> 00:20:58,228
<i>of this milk has passed quite awhile ago...</i>

295
00:21:00,807 --> 00:21:03,537
<i>He'll get sick if he drink this.</i>

296
00:21:04,678 --> 00:21:07,044
<i>It seems like that things are</i>
<i>going to get disastrous.</i>

297
00:21:14,988 --> 00:21:17,821
What the heck is going on?!

298
00:22:53,041 --> 00:22:54,065
What is going on?!

299
00:22:54,410 --> 00:22:56,844
This isn't the same Kakashi Sensei
from yesterday.

300
00:22:57,279 --> 00:22:59,008
Is this really the same Kakashi Sensei

301
00:22:59,081 --> 00:23:01,914
who got caught in my trap
and breezily came late?

302
00:23:02,451 --> 00:23:03,884
Damn it! Damn it!

303
00:23:04,119 --> 00:23:05,586
No way am I giving up!

304
00:23:05,988 --> 00:23:10,084
I'll defeat him and clear
this super difficult testl!

305
00:23:10,259 --> 00:23:12,819
No way am I going back now!

306
00:23:13,362 --> 00:23:15,762
Next episode:
"Pass or Fail: Survival Test"

307
00:23:16,031 --> 00:23:18,022
Don't miss my outstanding performance!
